<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 22:06:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“在学术文献中，犹太人以具有高度的适应力而闻名”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-jewish-people-are-known-in-academic-literature-to-have-high-resilience/0000018b-2598-d3fc-a3bf-bffd91d90000</link><description>梅厄·埃尔兰准将研究灾难后社会和社区的重建方式。哈马斯发动可怕的袭击后不久，当未来显得比以往任何时候都更加黑暗时，他设法找到了乐观的小理由</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 21:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-jewish-people-are-known-in-academic-literature-to-have-high-resilience/0000018b-2598-d3fc-a3bf-bffd91d90000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，特朗普询问主要亲以色列盟友是否可以在哈马斯袭击后呼吁“立即弹劾”内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/trump-wants-netanyahu-impeached-over-hamas-attacks-rolling-stone-reports/0000018b-2592-d680-af9b-27de3c360000</link><description>该报告发布前几个小时，特朗普公开批评内塔尼亚胡和以色列情报机构允许哈马斯袭击发生，并指出如果 2020 年选举没有“操纵”，这种袭击永远不会发生</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 20:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/trump-wants-netanyahu-impeached-over-hamas-attacks-rolling-stone-reports/0000018b-2592-d680-af9b-27de3c360000</guid></item><item><title>“他们向我开枪，爸爸，”我儿子说。我必须尽力拯救他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theyre-shooting-at-me-dad-my-son-said-i-had-to-try-to-save-him/0000018b-2529-d680-af9b-27ef90b60000</link><description>我问我的儿子，他当时正在被哈马斯袭击的超新星狂欢节上，他的确切位置在哪里，我根本不明白他在说什么，我说：“我来了，我来了。”我听到背景中有枪声，电话就被挂断了</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 20:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theyre-shooting-at-me-dad-my-son-said-i-had-to-try-to-save-him/0000018b-2529-d680-af9b-27ef90b60000</guid></item><item><title>在超新星音乐节上，“恐怖分子在各个方向等着我们”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-the-supernova-music-festival-terrorists-were-waiting-for-us-in-every-direction/0000018b-2477-d680-af9b-26ff158c0000</link><description>超新星恍惚节现场的混乱和恐怖已经消失，取而代之的是军事效率。一名返回的幸存者讲述了他的故事</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 20:05:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-the-supernova-music-festival-terrorists-were-waiting-for-us-in-every-direction/0000018b-2477-d680-af9b-26ff158c0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯呼吁“愤怒日”后，以色列敦促海外公民避免抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-urges-citizens-abroad-to-avoid-protests-after-hamas-calls-for-day-of-rage/0000018b-256c-d3fc-a3bf-bfed68730000</link><description>哈马斯领导层于 13 日星期五呼吁全球抗议并伤害以色列人和犹太人，以色列敦促海外公民保持警惕并避免集会</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 19:56:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-urges-citizens-abroad-to-avoid-protests-after-hamas-calls-for-day-of-rage/0000018b-256c-d3fc-a3bf-bfed68730000</guid></item><item><title>就连以色列总统也不知道以色列对加沙的计划是什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-12/ty-article/.highlight/even-israels-president-doesnt-know-what-israels-plan-for-gaza-is/0000018b-251a-d680-af9b-27dedbf40000</link><description>当以色列领导人不得不询问媒体对哈马斯和加沙的计划时，未来看起来非常非常黑暗</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 19:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-12/ty-article/.highlight/even-israels-president-doesnt-know-what-israels-plan-for-gaza-is/0000018b-251a-d680-af9b-27dedbf40000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯表示，哈马斯袭击中以色列受害者的照片“超出了我们所能理解和消化的范围”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/blinken-images-of-israeli-victims-beyond-anything-we-can-comprehend-and-digest/0000018b-24f9-d010-a59f-bdf9e1a00000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在对以色列进行声援访问时表示，“这让人想起伊斯兰国”。 “如果图像值一千个字，那么这些图像可能值一百万个字”</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 18:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/blinken-images-of-israeli-victims-beyond-anything-we-can-comprehend-and-digest/0000018b-24f9-d010-a59f-bdf9e1a00000</guid></item><item><title>“返回以色列并不是一个困难的决定。我们不能逃跑而把所有人抛在后面”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-12/ty-article/.highlight/returning-to-israel-wasnt-a-difficult-decision-we-cant-run-and-leave-everyone-behind/0000018b-2512-d010-a59f-bd73b1f50000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：在加沙战争期间决定返回以色列的人们，以及决定离开以色列的其他人</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 18:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-12/ty-article/.highlight/returning-to-israel-wasnt-a-difficult-decision-we-cant-run-and-leave-everyone-behind/0000018b-2512-d010-a59f-bd73b1f50000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击前一天晚上，以色列军队高层收到了令人不安的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-top-brass-received-troubling-info-night-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-24e2-d680-af9b-26eed7b10000</link><description>信息片段促使以色列安全部门和辛贝特负责人进行了电话磋商，从而引发了更多讨论。会谈结束，决定不提高警戒级别</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 18:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-top-brass-received-troubling-info-night-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-24e2-d680-af9b-26eed7b10000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列各地，犹太人和阿拉伯人联手帮助战争受害者并防止骚乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/across-israel-jews-and-arabs-join-forces-to-help-war-victims-and-prevent-riots/0000018b-24d1-d680-af9b-26dfc6d00000</link><description>在海法和雅法，犹太人和阿拉伯人联合巡逻，力图防止双方发生暴力事件。在南部，贝都因居民冒着生命危险寻找哈马斯恐怖活动的受害者。在战争的阴影下，阿拉伯犹太人团结倡议浮出水面</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 18:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/across-israel-jews-and-arabs-join-forces-to-help-war-victims-and-prevent-riots/0000018b-24d1-d680-af9b-26dfc6d00000</guid></item><item><title>波兰大使馆在波兰选举前取消对以色列境内波兰人的投票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/polish-embassy-cancels-ability-vote-for-poles-in-israel-in-sundays-polish-elections/0000018b-2418-dd34-afdf-f59fda5c0000</link><description>据波兰驻以色列大使馆称，由于安全原因，投票的可能性被取消。现代东欧历史学家表示，在上次大选中，“民主反对派在海外投票的波兰人中大获全胜”</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 17:26:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/polish-embassy-cancels-ability-vote-for-poles-in-israel-in-sundays-polish-elections/0000018b-2418-dd34-afdf-f59fda5c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列灵魂的拆除承包商</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/the-demolition-contractor-of-the-israeli-soul/0000018b-24ad-d3fc-a3bf-bfedadff0000</link><description>在以色列变成内塔尼亚胡之前几秒钟，它发生了</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 16:32:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/the-demolition-contractor-of-the-israeli-soul/0000018b-24ad-d3fc-a3bf-bfedadff0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯突袭以色列的新战线：经济恐怖主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/a-new-front-joins-hamas-surprise-attack-in-israel-economic-terrorism/0000018b-2444-d3fc-a3bf-bfed8f480000</link><description>哈马斯袭击伤亡者的家属报告称，他们用亲人的账户购买了价值数千谢克尔的商品</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 16:24:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/a-new-front-joins-hamas-surprise-attack-in-israel-economic-terrorism/0000018b-2444-d3fc-a3bf-bfed8f480000</guid></item><item><title>在一切地狱爆发之前，以色列最美丽的地方之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/one-of-the-most-beautiful-parts-of-israel-before-all-hell-broke-loose/0000018b-1f47-df31-a99f-7fc75fa20000</link><description>雷伊姆派对上被屠杀的狂欢者逃往的牛油果林，以及数十名人质被扣押在附近的贝里火山口，都在提醒人们内盖夫西部是多么美丽——以及它重返家园的希望是多么巨大。成为大屠杀现场之前的情况</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 16:15:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/one-of-the-most-beautiful-parts-of-israel-before-all-hell-broke-loose/0000018b-1f47-df31-a99f-7fc75fa20000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击以色列后，特朗普的内塔尼亚胡倒刺暴露了共和党的杀戮欲望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/trumps-netanyahu-barbs-betray-gop-bloodlust-after-hamas-attacks-on-israel/0000018b-2412-dd34-afdf-f5970b2a0000</link><description>特朗普的言论虽然具有煽动性和麻木不仁，但在很大程度上与共和党对以色列的态度及其在加沙的持续反应脱节</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 15:24:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/trumps-netanyahu-barbs-betray-gop-bloodlust-after-hamas-attacks-on-israel/0000018b-2412-dd34-afdf-f5970b2a0000</guid></item><item><title>教育部长称以色列政府将对哈马斯袭击事件承担责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/israels-government-will-be-held-accountable-for-hamas-attack-education-minister-says/0000018b-2407-dd34-afdf-f587246d0000</link><description>在高级联盟成员避免公开露面的六天后，约夫·基什表示，“这件事发生在我们的政府领导下，我们将得出结论，我们将承担责任。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 15:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/israels-government-will-be-held-accountable-for-hamas-attack-education-minister-says/0000018b-2407-dd34-afdf-f587246d0000</guid></item><item><title>“你们让我们失望了”：希伯来大学猛烈抨击哈佛大学和斯坦福大学对以色列人大屠杀的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-slams-harvard-stanford-for-responses-to-massacre-of-israelis/0000018b-242e-d680-af9b-26ee50e60000</link><description>以色列大学猛烈抨击哈佛的一封学生信，该信被视为为哈马斯的谋杀辩护，而斯坦福大学就袭击事件发表的声明“不符合道德领导力的最低标准”</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 14:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-slams-harvard-stanford-for-responses-to-massacre-of-israelis/0000018b-242e-d680-af9b-26ee50e60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的英以人质儿童在伦敦新闻发布会上乞求归还</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/london-based-children-of-british-israeli-captives-in-gaza-beg-for-their-return/0000018b-23d5-dd34-afdf-f7d709bd0000</link><description>“我们首先对屠杀和破坏说不……我们有工作要做；我们有人要带回来，”被加沙武装分子从基布兹尼尔·奥兹绑架的英国-以色列国民的孩子们在激动人心的新闻发布会上说道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 14:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/london-based-children-of-british-israeli-captives-in-gaza-beg-for-their-return/0000018b-23d5-dd34-afdf-f7d709bd0000</guid></item><item><title>我84岁的母亲被扣为人质。我也以她的名义恳求：不要摧毁加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/my-84-year-old-mother-was-taken-hostage-in-her-name-too-i-plead-dont-destroy-gaza/0000018b-2432-dd34-afdf-f5b777c50000</link><description>我的母亲和她在尼尔奥兹基布兹遭到屠杀的许多朋友都是和平人士，他们相信在边境围栏的另一边也有享有权利的人</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 14:19:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/my-84-year-old-mother-was-taken-hostage-in-her-name-too-i-plead-dont-destroy-gaza/0000018b-2432-dd34-afdf-f5b777c50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的阿拉伯公民在以色列和巴勒斯坦无辜受害者之间左右为难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-citizens-torn-between-innocent-israeli-and-palestinians-victims/0000018b-23a5-dd34-afdf-f7a72ca90000</link><description>对于以色列的许多阿拉伯人来说，目睹许多无辜以色列人在一侧受到伤害的悲伤很快变成了看到许多无辜者在加沙地带遭到袭击的痛苦</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 14:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-citizens-torn-between-innocent-israeli-and-palestinians-victims/0000018b-23a5-dd34-afdf-f7a72ca90000</guid></item></channel></rss>